Business Brief -- Consumat Systems Inc.:
   Environmental Systems Co.
   To Sell Stake in Company
Environmental Systems also said that as of Dec. 31, its
outstanding loan to Consumat was in default. The company said
it has outstanding demand loans of $2 million from Consumat.
   Environmental Systems said it is evaluating possible
action with respect to the loan, including but not limited to
a restructuring of the loan or the institution of legal
proceedings against Consumat.